FL,326,320,120,260,000,100
PN,32505
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F325A1784733509
OL,3,CRemembering Britain's first Black
OL,4,Cpoliceman
OL,6,FCarlisle MP Julie Minns said: "I want
OL,7,FJohn Kent to have a blue plaque here
OL,8,Fin Carlisle, ideally where he would
OL,9,Fhave lived on the old police station
OL,10,Fin the centre of town.
OL,12,F"But I even want to go a bit further
OL,13,Fthan that. I think it would be amazing
OL,14,Fif we had a portrait hanging in the
OL,15,FNational Portrait Gallery of Britain's
OL,16,Ffirst black police officer."
OL,18,FMs Minns added that the application to
OL,19,Fhave a blue plaque dedicated to John
OL,20,FKent is underway with Historic England.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G5/6
